\n中華民國刑法第276條\r\n因過失致人於死者，處5年以下有期徒刑、拘役或50萬元以下罰\r\n金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/110%2c%e4%ba%a4%e8%a8%b4%2c5%2c20210924%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,110,交訴,5,20210924,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"交訴","JNO":"5","JDATE":"20210924","JTITLE":"過失致死"}